  "text": "We’re excited to announce that the program for The EuroPython Beginners' Day Unconference is now available! \n\nJoin us on 19 July 2025 at WPP Prague, Bubenská 1, 170 00 Praha 7-Holešovice, for a day designed especially for newcomers to tech. Here’s a sneak peek at what you can expect:\n\n➡️ Panel Discussion: How to Succeed in a Junior Role – Hear real stories from junior developers and join the conversation yourself.\n➡️ Panel Discussion: Landing A Great Job – Get insider tips from recruiters and engineering leaders on what makes candidates stand out.\n➡️ Discussion Circle: Junior vs. Senior – Explore both sides of the journey and share your perspective in an open, empathetic forum.\n\nWe're proud to share that the event is organized in a cooperation between EuroPython and Junior Guru — a club created by Honza Javorek to support juniors in IT on their path.\n\nStay tuned for more information about our guest panelists!\n\nReady to take part? Register now—link in the first comment.\n\n#EuroPython #BeginnersDay #PythonCommunity #TechCareers #Prague2025 #EuroPython2025",
